      "source_requirement": "If the location is valid, the user can choose what to check such as temperature, humidity, rainfall, pressure, or dew point.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall allow a user to choose what to check (temperature, humidity, rainfall, pressure, or dew point) if the entered location is valid."
    },
